---
// Section 02 — Brand statement. Pure typography.
---
<section class="section statement">
  <div class="wrap statement-inner">
    <span class="mono mission-id" data-reveal>BRAND STATEMENT / SYS-02</span>
    <div class="statement-rule" data-reveal></div>
    <h2 class="display" data-reveal data-delay="0.05">One toolkit.<br/>A lot of ground covered.</h2>
    <p class="lead" data-reveal data-delay="0.1">
      Spacedog is built to move across disciplines without losing clarity.
      We scale ideas, shape productions, and bring creative to life without
      overcomplicating the process.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .statement { padding-block: var(--space-2xl); }
  .statement-inner { max-width: 760px; }
  .statement-rule { height: 1px; background: var(--color-purple); width: 64px; margin: 16px 0 var(--space-md); }
  .statement h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
</style>
